      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖牌子〗。众人同下。四短刀、四长枪、武承嗣同上。〖牌子〗。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006048_e00030",
